data.meta_description: The Rensselaer County Office of the District Attorney maintains a team of professional and experienced prosecutors who are committed to equal justice under the law, pursuant to the oath to the people of the State of New York.
data.text:
The Rensselaer County Office of the District Attorney maintains a team of professional and experienced prosecutors who are committed to equal justice under the law, pursuant to the oath to the people of the State of New York. Town courts are listed with the Assistant District Attorney (ADA) responsible.
